 Products 












PERI Products and Systems
Well thought-out. Efficient. Proven.







Products and Systems
PERI products are characterized through their innovative design, intelligent mechanical features and practical details – manufactured with high quality standards and thus ideally suited for dealing with the tough everyday use on the construction site.







 Formwork Systems







Formwork Systems
PERI Formwork Solutions: for high-rise buildings with complex shapes, for challenging bridge and tunnel structures, for the implementation of the highest architectural concrete requirements and even more.
 


 Scaffolding and Shoring Systems







Scaffolding Systems
With the experience gained from countless global scaffolding projects, our scaffold experts enableour customers to realize projects with PERI UP scaffolding constructions both economically and safely.
 


 Services







Services
The service we provide simply does not end with the delivery. With our services, in particular, we accompany and support our clients throughout the entire project.
 






 Plywood and Components







Plywood and Components
PERI offers an extensive range plywood various grades and sizes.
 


 Software







Software
The software solution myPERI allows tracking and monitoring of material on your jobsite as well as reviewing billing information, drawings and other information.
 







